creator: Oasis Outsourcing Inc.
descriptionHtml: The Oasis TimeKeeper kiosk app enables TimeKeeper clients to turn an Android device into a working time clock for their employees to record their time and perform other self-service options. Employees can quickly punch in/out, punch for lunches and breaks, and perform job transfers, even when the device is in a location without an established cellular or Wi-Fi signal. Employers can grant employees access to enter pay adjustments, request time off, view their schedule, and view/approve their time card. Clients can enable an optional image-capture setting during the time of a punch, or enable facial recognition to eliminate buddy punching.
